      provincia - The province of the Colegio. String.
      localidad - The locality of the Colegio. String.
      denominacion - The denomination of the Colegio. String.
      naturaleza - The nature of the Colegio. String.
      comedor - The dining status of the Colegio. Boolean.

      web - The web address of the Colegio. String.
      descripcion - The description of the Colegio. String.
      direccion - The address of the Colegio. String.
      telefono - The phone number of the Colegio. String.
      imagenes - The list of images associated with the Colegio. List of Imagen objects.
      ofertas - The list of offers associated with the Colegio. List of Oferta objects.
      usuario - The user associated with the Colegio. Usuario object.
      comentarios - The list of comments associated with the Colegio. List of Comentario objects.
      valoraciones - The list of ratings associated with the Colegio. List of Valoracion objects.
      respuestas - The list of responses associated with the Colegio. List of Respuesta objects.
      codigo - The code of the Colegio. String.
      activo - The active status of the Colegio. Boolean.

      public void removeComentario(Comentario comentario)
